the pickdeadline is never updated in the database
treatments are never filled in PackCard
the player view endpoint can be used to see any players view point (change to remove playerId and instead use ClaimsPrinciple)

// maybe look at this
generalise the pack generation to work with other sets
GenerateSingleECLPack or GenerateSingleEOEPack or GenerateSingleMOMPack

contains
generateCommons(Set set, int amount)
generateUncommons(Set set, int amount, int specialprintWeighting)
generateWildcard(Set set, Chances cardChances) - Chances has weighings for C U R M cards
this will make it more scalable when implementing other sets

packs will generally contain 
6 commons
have a chance for a special guest in the 7th common slot
3 uncommons with a chance for a special printing
a wildcard with varied rarity weighting
rare / mythic with special printing
trad foil of any rarity
a land card



